    • Location

      public Location(String address1, String address2, String address3, String city, String zipCode, String country, String state, List<String> displayAddress)
      Constructs a Location with detailed address information.
      Parameters:
      address1 - The primary street address.
      address2 - Additional address information, such as suite or apartment number.
      address3 - Further address details.
      city - The city in which the restaurant is located.
      zipCode - The postal code for the location.
      country - The country of the restaurant.
      state - The state or province of the restaurant.
      displayAddress - A list of strings that form the complete displayable address.
